1
00:00:21,890 --> 00:00:26,370
(X Theater)

2
00:01:34,340 --> 00:01:35,190
Mengmeng,

3
00:01:36,340 --> 00:01:37,630
do you know?

4
00:01:38,830 --> 00:01:41,270
Everyone is a star in the sky.

5
00:01:50,910 --> 00:01:53,340
Then which one are you?

6
00:01:55,110 --> 00:01:57,110
The brightest one is me.

7
00:01:58,910 --> 00:02:00,990
When I'm not by your side,

8
00:02:02,630 --> 00:02:04,830
the brightest star
will keep you company.

9
00:02:09,270 --> 00:02:13,180
What if I want to talk to you?

10
00:02:18,110 --> 00:02:20,420
Just call out my name

11
00:02:20,900 --> 00:02:22,550
to the brightest star.

12
00:02:23,350 --> 00:02:25,270
If it is twinkling,

13
00:02:25,830 --> 00:02:27,740
it means I've heard you.

14
00:02:28,620 --> 00:02:30,830
Then you can talk to me.

15
00:02:35,350 --> 00:02:37,830
Mom, is that you?

16
00:02:39,300 --> 00:02:40,300
Yes.

17
00:02:43,990 --> 00:02:45,140
Mom,

18
00:02:45,140 --> 00:02:47,110
is it you?

19
00:02:48,550 --> 00:02:49,670
Mom,

20
00:02:50,270 --> 00:02:53,700
I don't want you to turn into a star,

21
00:02:53,990 --> 00:02:56,700
but I'll be good.

22
00:03:05,580 --> 00:03:07,020
Good girl.

23
00:03:12,550 --> 00:03:13,580
Mengmeng,

24
00:03:14,270 --> 00:03:16,300
promise me one thing.

25
00:03:17,270 --> 00:03:18,580
What is it?

26
00:03:21,700 --> 00:03:24,270
Treat Auntie Hong as your mom.

27
00:03:25,990 --> 00:03:27,270
Why?

28
00:03:30,420 --> 00:03:32,990
When I'm not by your side,

29
00:03:33,550 --> 00:03:35,510
Aunt Hong will take care of you.

30
00:03:36,670 --> 00:03:39,110
She will treat you as well as I do.

31
00:03:41,020 --> 00:03:43,830
Can you also treat her as your mom?

32
00:03:50,270 --> 00:03:52,990
What if I want you to promise that?

33
00:04:03,110 --> 00:04:05,550
I hope you will grow up happily,

34
00:04:06,990 --> 00:04:08,580
meet good people,

35
00:04:10,990 --> 00:04:12,700
and live a long life,

36
00:04:14,020 --> 00:04:15,140
okay?

37
00:04:27,580 --> 00:04:33,340
=Persona=
=Episode 12=

38
00:04:55,820 --> 00:04:56,790
Danshun.

39
00:05:00,350 --> 00:05:01,260
What's wrong?

40
00:05:04,150 --> 00:05:05,670
I want to eat cotton candy.

41
00:05:06,030 --> 00:05:07,470
Will you buy it for me?

42
00:05:09,230 --> 00:05:10,420
Now?

43
00:05:13,710 --> 00:05:14,590
Okay.

44
00:05:15,230 --> 00:05:16,350
I'll go now.

45
00:05:24,590 --> 00:05:25,550
Danshun.

46
00:05:41,110 --> 00:05:42,030
The keys.

47
00:05:46,150 --> 00:05:47,590
You'll be at home, right?

48
00:05:48,150 --> 00:05:49,420
Go back and rest.

49
00:06:11,910 --> 00:06:12,790
Here, take it.

50
00:06:14,150 --> 00:06:15,910
You can only have one more.

51
00:06:24,350 --> 00:06:25,230
Two cotton candies.

52
00:06:25,230 --> 00:06:26,590
Okay, one for five yuan.

53
00:06:34,260 --> 00:06:35,590
Does it stick to your teeth?

54
00:06:36,790 --> 00:06:38,230
- Tasty.
- Is it sweet?

55
00:06:39,550 --> 00:06:40,670
Try mine.

56
00:06:43,790 --> 00:06:45,350
You can't eat anymore, okay?

57
00:06:45,350 --> 00:06:46,190
Okay.

58
00:06:46,670 --> 00:06:48,590
Look, you've eaten this down so small.

59
00:06:49,790 --> 00:06:51,230
Shall we lift you?

60
00:06:52,030 --> 00:06:52,870
Sure.

61
00:06:55,260 --> 00:06:56,530
Hold my hand.

62
00:06:57,350 --> 00:06:58,350
Let me lift you high.

63
00:06:58,590 --> 00:06:59,790
One, two, three, fly.

64
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:03,060
Are you happy?

65
00:07:04,340 --> 00:07:05,620
Did you eat it today?

66
00:07:07,150 --> 00:07:07,990
Hurry up.

67
00:07:08,110 --> 00:07:08,950
Okay.

68
00:07:34,590 --> 00:07:35,910
I'm back, Zhang Yan.

69
00:08:18,260 --> 00:08:19,110
Zhang Yan?

70
00:09:01,780 --> 00:09:02,660
Zhang Yan.

71
00:09:06,310 --> 00:09:07,430
Zhang Yan.

72
00:09:15,540 --> 00:09:16,430
Danshun,

73
00:09:16,780 --> 00:09:18,070
please forgive me.

74
00:09:19,020 --> 00:09:21,310
I don't have the courage
to leave in front of you,

75
00:09:22,020 --> 00:09:23,800
so I chose to leave
without saying goodbye.

76
00:09:25,860 --> 00:09:28,070
The first time you took me
to Zhuyun Temple,

77
00:09:28,430 --> 00:09:30,430
you bought cotton candy for each of us.

78
00:09:31,190 --> 00:09:32,950
You treat yourself

79
00:09:33,190 --> 00:09:35,020
and others like a child.

80
00:09:35,780 --> 00:09:37,190
It makes me feel very special

81
00:09:37,190 --> 00:09:38,310
and happy.

82
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,950
That was actually
the first time I tasted

83
00:09:40,950 --> 00:09:42,310
the flavor of cotton candy.

84
00:09:43,260 --> 00:09:44,740
I will never forget it.

85
00:09:46,140 --> 00:09:47,780
Later, we fell in love.

86
00:09:48,140 --> 00:09:49,900
I realized you truly have
a loving heart.

87
00:09:53,020 --> 00:09:54,380
To this day, I still feel

88
00:09:54,780 --> 00:09:55,900
I'm so lucky to have met you

89
00:09:57,380 --> 00:09:59,020
and fallen in love with you.

90
00:10:02,260 --> 00:10:04,660
A monk from Zhuyun Temple once told me

91
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:07,190
that people in this world

92
00:10:07,500 --> 00:10:09,430
can't let go of many things.

93
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,380
But the journey of life

94
00:10:11,380 --> 00:10:13,190
is about letting go little by little,

95
00:10:14,140 --> 00:10:16,780
or the burden will be too heavy
for them to go on.

96
00:10:18,540 --> 00:10:20,430
What you and Hong did for me

97
00:10:20,660 --> 00:10:23,430
was help a dying person
lay down a heavy burden

98
00:10:23,740 --> 00:10:25,530
and let go of attachment
to the mortal world,

99
00:10:26,380 --> 00:10:27,780
so I can go on living

100
00:10:27,950 --> 00:10:28,860
and loving others

101
00:10:29,020 --> 00:10:30,780
as Mengmeng's mother.

102
00:10:34,260 --> 00:10:35,500
I am very grateful.

103
00:10:36,540 --> 00:10:37,500
Danshun,

104
00:10:37,900 --> 00:10:40,020
those cotton candies are for you.

105
00:10:41,780 --> 00:10:43,380
Your days are still long.

106
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:46,020
(Alprazolam Tablets)
Whether you remember me or forget me

107
00:10:46,020 --> 00:10:47,020
doesn't matter.

108
00:10:48,430 --> 00:10:49,430
No matter what,

109
00:10:49,430 --> 00:10:50,950
keep going.

110
00:10:52,140 --> 00:10:53,540
If it feels too bitter,

111
00:10:54,660 --> 00:10:56,430
have a bite of cotton candy.

112
00:11:18,780 --> 00:11:19,950
What day is it today?

113
00:11:20,260 --> 00:11:21,380
Why make it so grand?

114
00:11:25,260 --> 00:11:26,780
The 150,000 you lent me

115
00:11:26,780 --> 00:11:27,900
is all on the card.

116
00:11:28,540 --> 00:11:29,430
You can have it back.

117
00:11:33,740 --> 00:11:34,900
What about the surgery?

118
00:11:36,900 --> 00:11:37,740
I'll still have one,

119
00:11:37,950 --> 00:11:39,540
but I won't be using your money.

120
00:11:42,620 --> 00:11:43,780
What does this mean?

121
00:11:46,380 --> 00:11:47,620
It doesn't mean anything.

122
00:11:50,860 --> 00:11:51,780
Ma Weicheng,

123
00:11:53,260 --> 00:11:54,430
let's break up.

124
00:11:58,780 --> 00:12:00,140
I've given the money back to you.

125
00:12:00,780 --> 00:12:01,950
We're even now.

126
00:12:06,070 --> 00:12:07,630
You don't have to look at me like that.

127
00:12:08,540 --> 00:12:11,430
I know that in your heart,
I'm a casual woman

128
00:12:12,190 --> 00:12:13,380
who doesn't deserve love.

129
00:12:13,860 --> 00:12:15,020
What are you talking about?

130
00:12:15,190 --> 00:12:16,620
I've never said that.

131
00:12:17,020 --> 00:12:18,660
But that's exactly what you think.

132
00:12:20,300 --> 00:12:21,140
Do you still love me?

133
00:12:21,140 --> 00:12:22,070
I love you.

134
00:12:22,750 --> 00:12:23,620
I've always loved you.

135
00:12:23,620 --> 00:12:24,660
What do you love about me?

136
00:12:32,190 --> 00:12:33,140
Lin Chang,

137
00:12:34,540 --> 00:12:36,900
on the first day
you appeared in this alley,

138
00:12:37,660 --> 00:12:39,070
you were drenched all over.

139
00:12:39,070 --> 00:12:40,780
I felt that you were very pitiful.

140
00:12:41,540 --> 00:12:43,380
Then you said you wanted
to go to Haizi Cliff.

141
00:12:43,900 --> 00:12:44,780
I didn't even tell you

142
00:12:44,780 --> 00:12:46,540
that I pulled some strings.

143
00:12:46,540 --> 00:12:49,140
Only then were we able to walk in
through that small path.

144
00:12:50,020 --> 00:12:51,620
On that cliff, you said

145
00:12:52,070 --> 00:12:53,600
you wanted to find someone to rely on.

146
00:12:53,660 --> 00:12:55,140
At that moment, I made up my mind.

147
00:12:55,430 --> 00:12:56,900
I really wanted to protect you.

148
00:12:59,260 --> 00:13:00,740
You told me you have heart disease.

149
00:13:01,430 --> 00:13:02,540
I tried every possible way

150
00:13:02,540 --> 00:13:04,660
to find the best doctor to treat you.

151
00:13:07,780 --> 00:13:10,070
I even managed to find 150,000 yuan.

152
00:13:10,620 --> 00:13:11,900
It wasn't easy for me.

153
00:13:16,310 --> 00:13:17,190
I think loving someone

154
00:13:17,190 --> 00:13:19,430
means giving everything I have to them.

155
00:13:21,380 --> 00:13:22,900
That's exactly how I treated you.

156
00:13:26,020 --> 00:13:28,140
So, that's what you've been thinking.

157
00:13:41,860 --> 00:13:42,780
I know

158
00:13:43,540 --> 00:13:45,140
you've been mad lately.

159
00:13:46,660 --> 00:13:48,310
Let's just be open about it.

160
00:13:48,880 --> 00:13:49,740
Don't be upset.

161
00:13:49,740 --> 00:13:50,580
Okay?

162
00:13:54,780 --> 00:13:55,740
So touched.

163
00:13:59,260 --> 00:14:00,310
You won't end up

164
00:14:00,310 --> 00:14:02,020
moving yourself while acting, right?

165
00:14:09,260 --> 00:14:10,500
I really want to ask you:

166
00:14:11,160 --> 00:14:12,140
Every time you talk to me

167
00:14:12,140 --> 00:14:14,190
so affectionately,

168
00:14:14,430 --> 00:14:15,500
do you think you are

169
00:14:16,190 --> 00:14:17,260
especially affectionate,

170
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:18,860
handsome,

171
00:14:18,860 --> 00:14:20,430
and charming?

172
00:14:20,660 --> 00:14:22,900
Any woman would be
completely captivated by you,

173
00:14:23,540 --> 00:14:24,380
right?

174
00:14:25,310 --> 00:14:27,430
What do you mean
by giving unconditionally?

175
00:14:27,430 --> 00:14:28,770
Wasn't this 150,000 lent to me?

176
00:14:28,770 --> 00:14:30,260
If it's lent, shouldn't it be repaid?

177
00:14:30,260 --> 00:14:31,740
How is that unconditional?

178
00:14:33,020 --> 00:14:33,900
The things you did

179
00:14:33,900 --> 00:14:35,260
were just to make me listen to you,

180
00:14:35,260 --> 00:14:36,460
so you can control me, right?

181
00:14:37,310 --> 00:14:38,150
Also,

182
00:14:38,430 --> 00:14:39,310
you love me?

183
00:14:39,430 --> 00:14:40,950
You love me, so you hit me?

184
00:14:41,070 --> 00:14:42,500
What kind of nonsense is that?

185
00:14:42,500 --> 00:14:43,430
Don't lie to me

186
00:14:43,430 --> 00:14:45,020
in the name of love, okay?

187
00:14:45,020 --> 00:14:46,900
- Stop talking.
- Why should I?

188
00:14:48,140 --> 00:14:49,780
You can't handle it now?

189
00:14:52,140 --> 00:14:54,020
Do you really think women are

190
00:14:54,020 --> 00:14:55,900
all stupid enough to be fooled by you?

191
00:14:55,950 --> 00:14:57,020
Listen.

192
00:14:57,260 --> 00:14:59,430
They didn't get fooled
because of stupidity

193
00:14:59,430 --> 00:15:00,620
but kindness.

194
00:15:00,780 --> 00:15:02,260
But I'm not kind.

195
00:15:02,260 --> 00:15:03,430
What can you do?

196
00:15:13,500 --> 00:15:15,380
What else can you do
besides hitting women?

197
00:15:18,060 --> 00:15:19,430
When you were punched by Mr. Wang,

198
00:15:19,430 --> 00:15:20,580
you didn't even dare to fart.

199
00:15:20,580 --> 00:15:22,150
I told you to stop talking.

200
00:15:22,780 --> 00:15:24,260
Let me talk!

201
00:15:26,140 --> 00:15:28,020
You're nothing outside.

202
00:15:28,310 --> 00:15:30,020
All you do is hit women at home.

203
00:15:30,660 --> 00:15:32,740
What right do you have
to look down on me?

204
00:15:32,740 --> 00:15:35,070
Why can't you just listen to me?

205
00:15:36,260 --> 00:15:37,430
Ma Weicheng,

206
00:15:37,660 --> 00:15:39,260
you're a useless man.

207
00:16:00,070 --> 00:16:01,190
My medicine.

208
00:16:02,540 --> 00:16:03,180
I...

209
00:16:03,270 --> 00:16:04,310
My heart disease medicine.

210
00:16:04,310 --> 00:16:05,660
Don't pretend with me.

211
00:16:07,900 --> 00:16:09,020
My medicine.

212
00:16:11,430 --> 00:16:12,740
My medicine.

213
00:16:14,020 --> 00:16:15,380
Today,

214
00:16:15,380 --> 00:16:16,500
if I die here,

215
00:16:17,430 --> 00:16:18,310
you

216
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:19,340
will be

217
00:16:19,540 --> 00:16:20,620
a murderer.

218
00:16:23,140 --> 00:16:24,190
Give me the medicine.

219
00:16:29,740 --> 00:16:30,780
Where is your medicine?

220
00:16:57,020 --> 00:16:57,860
Wait here.

221
00:16:58,310 --> 00:16:59,620
I'll go get the medicine.

222
00:16:59,860 --> 00:17:00,780
Just wait here.

223
00:17:08,140 --> 00:17:10,820
(Tiantai'an Health Products)

224
00:17:17,500 --> 00:17:19,260
There is a back door
at Ma Weicheng's house.

225
00:17:19,780 --> 00:17:20,870
After he leaves,

226
00:17:21,060 --> 00:17:23,060
go around through the alley at the back.

227
00:18:13,020 --> 00:18:15,380
(Tiantai'an Health Products)

228
00:18:24,910 --> 00:18:27,230
Let a speculative and selfish coward

229
00:18:27,990 --> 00:18:29,890
choose the path we want him to take.

230
00:18:29,890 --> 00:18:31,100
Lin Chang, have your medicine.

231
00:18:31,100 --> 00:18:31,940
Here.

232
00:18:33,870 --> 00:18:35,100
Too easy.

233
00:18:38,230 --> 00:18:39,430
This is the choice

234
00:18:39,430 --> 00:18:41,190
Ma Weicheng will definitely make.

235
00:18:41,190 --> 00:18:42,910
(Tiantai'an Health Products)

236
00:18:42,910 --> 00:18:44,390
Zhang Yan knew him too well

237
00:18:46,190 --> 00:18:48,190
and predicted his every move,

238
00:18:50,390 --> 00:18:51,630
including disposing of the body.

239
00:19:37,150 --> 00:19:38,150
We

240
00:19:39,430 --> 00:19:41,500
never found Zhang Yan's body.

241
00:19:43,150 --> 00:19:45,060
Is it because Ma Weicheng

242
00:19:45,630 --> 00:19:48,060
disposed of the body at Haizi Cliff?

243
00:19:48,710 --> 00:19:49,990
Haizi Cliff

244
00:19:55,230 --> 00:19:57,630
is a place carefully chosen
by Zhang Yan.

245
00:19:58,820 --> 00:20:00,300
The tide rises there at night.

246
00:20:00,870 --> 00:20:02,100
Anything thrown down there

247
00:20:02,100 --> 00:20:03,630
will sink into the sea.

248
00:20:05,710 --> 00:20:07,580
When the tide recedes during the day,

249
00:20:10,300 --> 00:20:12,150
even the reefs will be exposed.

250
00:20:17,500 --> 00:20:19,230
We kept following Ma Weicheng.

251
00:20:20,740 --> 00:20:21,740
At the break of dawn,

252
00:20:22,190 --> 00:20:23,990
we pulled Zhang Yan out.

253
00:20:26,150 --> 00:20:28,340
Where did you hide the body?

254
00:20:35,100 --> 00:20:36,990
She's been laid to rest.

255
00:20:50,150 --> 00:20:51,190
Do you

256
00:20:53,300 --> 00:20:54,820
really believe

257
00:20:55,990 --> 00:20:58,870
that Qin Hong can keep living

258
00:21:00,230 --> 00:21:02,190
as Zhang Yan?

259
00:21:14,710 --> 00:21:17,150
That was Zhang Yan's final wish.

260
00:21:37,260 --> 00:21:40,900
(People's Police)

261
00:21:57,990 --> 00:21:58,450
Chief Liu,

262
00:21:58,470 --> 00:21:59,840
the colleague watching Feichuan

263
00:21:59,840 --> 00:22:00,970
found out that he arranged

264
00:22:00,970 --> 00:22:02,250
for a ship to go to sea.

265
00:22:02,500 --> 00:22:04,060
Going to sea during the fishing ban?

266
00:22:05,150 --> 00:22:06,470
Is he trying to leave the country?

267
00:22:06,670 --> 00:22:08,100
There's another matter, Chief Liu.

268
00:22:08,340 --> 00:22:09,630
The colleague tailing Ma Weicheng

269
00:22:09,950 --> 00:22:10,950
lost track of him.

270
00:22:16,330 --> 00:22:17,740
Notify the Coast Guard to move now.

271
00:22:17,740 --> 00:22:18,580
Yes.

272
00:22:31,340 --> 00:22:32,180
Zhou.

273
00:22:33,100 --> 00:22:33,940
Ma.

274
00:22:34,340 --> 00:22:35,710
You really managed to slip out.

275
00:22:36,740 --> 00:22:38,290
How do I get in touch with your friend?

276
00:22:38,580 --> 00:22:40,230
Ma, that's not very decent of you.

277
00:22:41,060 --> 00:22:42,530
You told me you ran into some trouble

278
00:22:42,530 --> 00:22:43,430
and had to leave.

279
00:22:43,430 --> 00:22:45,100
You never said this was about a murder.

280
00:22:46,470 --> 00:22:47,430
Don't talk nonsense.

281
00:22:48,150 --> 00:22:49,430
I didn't do that.

282
00:22:49,870 --> 00:22:51,150
Otherwise, why would I be here?

283
00:22:53,470 --> 00:22:54,580
You're so lucky.

284
00:22:54,820 --> 00:22:56,670
There happens to be a ship going out.

285
00:22:58,190 --> 00:22:59,190
If you can't come back,

286
00:22:59,580 --> 00:23:00,870
your store...

287
00:23:02,740 --> 00:23:04,090
I'll transfer it under your name.

288
00:23:09,670 --> 00:23:10,870
You didn't kill her, right?

289
00:23:33,910 --> 00:23:35,300
Hurry up.

290
00:23:57,500 --> 00:23:58,580
Get on the ship.

291
00:24:00,390 --> 00:24:01,390
If there's anyone

292
00:24:01,390 --> 00:24:02,430
who asks about me...

293
00:24:02,430 --> 00:24:03,630
Get on the ship.

294
00:24:03,630 --> 00:24:04,710
Please.

295
00:24:05,230 --> 00:24:06,470
From now on, you and I

296
00:24:06,470 --> 00:24:07,340
will be even,

297
00:24:07,740 --> 00:24:08,920
and so will Zhang Yan and I.

298
00:24:10,430 --> 00:24:11,740
Thank you on behalf of Zhang Yan.

299
00:24:12,910 --> 00:24:13,870
Come on, Mengmeng.

300
00:24:17,100 --> 00:24:18,430
Be careful, little girl.

301
00:24:32,430 --> 00:24:33,390
Hey, who is it?

302
00:24:52,630 --> 00:24:53,910
Find a room yourself.

303
00:25:15,740 --> 00:25:16,670
Go over there.

304
00:25:32,990 --> 00:25:35,190
Auntie, where are we going?

305
00:25:36,950 --> 00:25:39,190
We are going to a very faraway place.

306
00:25:39,390 --> 00:25:40,910
Are you scared?

307
00:25:44,230 --> 00:25:45,070
Well.

308
00:25:45,230 --> 00:25:46,100
Take a nap,

309
00:25:46,130 --> 00:25:47,390
and you won't be afraid anymore.

310
00:25:47,390 --> 00:25:48,300
Then we'll be there.

311
00:25:48,300 --> 00:25:49,190
Alright?

312
00:25:49,820 --> 00:25:51,300
I also have a secret weapon.

313
00:25:52,910 --> 00:25:54,500
This is a bravery candy.

314
00:25:54,500 --> 00:25:55,390
After eating it,

315
00:25:55,390 --> 00:25:56,580
you won't be afraid anymore.

316
00:25:56,580 --> 00:25:57,420
Give it a try.

317
00:25:59,670 --> 00:26:00,510
Okay?

318
00:26:21,150 --> 00:26:22,390
Oh, you're a friend of Zhou?

319
00:26:22,950 --> 00:26:24,470
- Hey.
- Go on.

320
00:26:24,470 --> 00:26:25,310
Come on.

321
00:26:25,430 --> 00:26:26,430
Go on.

322
00:26:26,430 --> 00:26:27,750
- Alright.
- Fu.

323
00:26:56,990 --> 00:26:57,530
Hey,

324
00:26:57,550 --> 00:26:58,820
are there still beds available?

325
00:26:58,910 --> 00:26:59,870
Go find one yourself.

326
00:27:25,910 --> 00:27:26,750
Hong.

327
00:27:27,580 --> 00:27:28,670
I beg you.

328
00:27:30,230 --> 00:27:31,630
Only you can help me.

329
00:27:32,850 --> 00:27:33,710
What about you?

330
00:27:33,710 --> 00:27:34,670
Go, go!

331
00:27:35,580 --> 00:27:36,420
Go!

332
00:28:08,710 --> 00:28:09,550
Mengmeng,

333
00:28:10,190 --> 00:28:11,430
I'll go out and take a look.

334
00:28:11,710 --> 00:28:13,910
Hold the little bunny
and sleep first, okay?

335
00:28:15,100 --> 00:28:15,940
Remember this:

336
00:28:15,950 --> 00:28:17,470
You can't go with anyone except me.

337
00:28:17,470 --> 00:28:18,310
Alright?

338
00:28:18,580 --> 00:28:19,430
Promise me.

339
00:28:19,430 --> 00:28:20,530
Come on, let's pinky swear.

340
00:28:23,870 --> 00:28:24,710
Go to sleep.

341
00:30:59,330 --> 00:31:00,500
How did I not think of that?

342
00:31:00,500 --> 00:31:02,150
You and Zhang Yan were in cahoots.

343
00:32:00,150 --> 00:32:01,150
Foolish women.

344
00:32:01,530 --> 00:32:02,390
One died in vain.

345
00:32:02,390 --> 00:32:04,150
And one will die at my hands today.

346
00:32:12,100 --> 00:32:14,180
(Police)

347
00:32:47,230 --> 00:32:48,900
Help! Help!

348
00:32:49,390 --> 00:32:50,700
No! No!

349
00:32:50,820 --> 00:32:51,670
Help!

350
00:32:57,990 --> 00:32:59,150
Help!

351
00:32:59,390 --> 00:33:00,230
Help!

352
00:33:03,230 --> 00:33:04,070
No!

353
00:33:05,670 --> 00:33:06,870
Help!

354
00:33:10,670 --> 00:33:11,520
Don't kill me.

355
00:33:11,580 --> 00:33:12,670
Don't kill me; I was wrong.

356
00:33:12,870 --> 00:33:13,710
I was wrong.

357
00:33:18,670 --> 00:33:19,670
Police! Don't move!

358
00:33:19,950 --> 00:33:20,990
Hands on your head! Squat!

359
00:33:21,190 --> 00:33:22,030
Don't move!

360
00:33:22,190 --> 00:33:23,470
Stop running! Stop!

361
00:33:23,470 --> 00:33:24,310
Don't move!

362
00:33:24,670 --> 00:33:25,680
- Come out!
- Come out!

363
00:33:28,710 --> 00:33:29,670
Don't move!

364
00:33:30,150 --> 00:33:30,990
Qin Hong.

365
00:34:30,990 --> 00:34:31,980
Hurry, go

366
00:34:34,910 --> 00:34:35,830
- Hurry.
- Hurry.

367
00:34:36,620 --> 00:34:37,550
Hurry, hurry.

368
00:34:52,700 --> 00:34:53,540
Mengmeng?

369
00:36:22,390 --> 00:36:23,310
Sorry.

370
00:36:32,540 --> 00:36:33,870
I owe you this.

371
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:35,620
For Kaifu.

372
00:36:46,350 --> 00:36:48,620
The law will give you a fair verdict.

373
00:36:56,470 --> 00:36:57,950
We all know about you

374
00:36:57,950 --> 00:36:59,310
and Zhang Yan now.

375
00:37:01,790 --> 00:37:03,060
You must believe in the law.

376
00:37:03,350 --> 00:37:04,750
It will punish Ma Weicheng.

377
00:37:06,020 --> 00:37:07,470
It will not let Zhang Yan down.

378
00:37:07,910 --> 00:37:09,180
After running for so long,

379
00:37:10,020 --> 00:37:11,060
I am tired.

380
00:37:12,580 --> 00:37:14,180
You've been looking for me for so long.

381
00:37:18,270 --> 00:37:19,430
You must be tired, too.

382
00:37:28,350 --> 00:37:29,270
Fortunately,

383
00:37:30,310 --> 00:37:31,700
we both feel at ease now.

384
00:37:50,620 --> 00:37:51,460
Mengmeng,

385
00:37:56,020 --> 00:37:57,910
I couldn't fulfill the promise

386
00:37:58,990 --> 00:38:00,430
I made to your mom.

387
00:38:00,990 --> 00:38:02,020
I'm sorry.

388
00:38:03,580 --> 00:38:05,430
I can't be there to watch you grow up.

389
00:39:15,430 --> 00:39:16,270
This is the place.

390
00:39:24,870 --> 00:39:26,470
(Combustion-style revenge)

391
00:39:26,470 --> 00:39:28,700
(can push the enemy into a sea of fire)

392
00:39:28,910 --> 00:39:30,220
(and also devour)

393
00:39:30,220 --> 00:39:33,620
(those beautiful memories
once buried inside.)

394
00:39:33,910 --> 00:39:35,470
(Even if Lyu Danshun, Qin Hong,)

395
00:39:35,470 --> 00:39:36,430
(and even Mengmeng)

396
00:39:36,700 --> 00:39:39,060
(could gain a moment of peace,)

397
00:39:39,700 --> 00:39:41,620
(they could not escape this ending)

398
00:39:41,830 --> 00:39:44,060
(when recalling Zhang Yan.)

399
00:39:45,220 --> 00:39:46,430
(From the very beginning,)

400
00:39:46,430 --> 00:39:47,870
(it was destined to be)

401
00:39:47,870 --> 00:39:49,750
(a tragedy that'd burn everything.)

402
00:39:56,220 --> 00:39:57,710
Chief Liu, we found her.

403
00:40:06,060 --> 00:40:10,140
(Pingtan First Detention Center)

404
00:41:25,340 --> 00:41:31,740
(Chen Yiting, Lyu Danshun)

405
00:41:31,740 --> 00:41:36,580
(Peace and good fortune)

406
00:41:53,780 --> 00:41:57,020
(Sacred and Time-honored,
Solemn and Serene)

407
00:42:10,340 --> 00:42:14,460
(Afterlife Tablet of Qin Desheng)

408
00:42:20,660 --> 00:42:23,580
(2002)

409
00:42:25,910 --> 00:42:26,750
Dad,

410
00:42:27,790 --> 00:42:29,780
there's not much left
in our old home in Chencang.

411
00:42:30,430 --> 00:42:32,150
You should spend more time
in the sun here.

412
00:42:33,740 --> 00:42:38,420
(Afterlife Tablet of Qin Desheng)

413
00:43:09,750 --> 00:43:10,590
Zhang Yan.

414
00:43:11,500 --> 00:43:12,340
Come back.

415
00:43:16,100 --> 00:43:16,990
Hurry up.

416
00:43:19,020 --> 00:43:20,220
Don't run around.

417
00:43:25,040 --> 00:43:31,280
♪Little hands holding starlight♪

418
00:43:31,660 --> 00:43:37,600
♪Giving it to the drooping flowers♪

419
00:43:38,250 --> 00:43:44,530
♪The wind cools the flower stems down♪

420
00:43:44,880 --> 00:43:51,420
♪Telling her not to fear the long night♪

421
00:43:54,780 --> 00:43:59,300
♪The fireflies gently sway♪

422
