(Qin Hong was sentenced to 18 years)

423
00:44:00,760 --> 00:44:02,950
(for intentional assault (death),
intentional assault,)

424
00:44:02,950 --> 00:44:04,540
(and attempted illegal border crossing.)

425
00:44:04,960 --> 00:44:06,100
(Ma Weicheng was sentenced)

426
00:44:06,100 --> 00:44:07,080
(to 20 years and fined)

427
00:44:07,080 --> 00:44:08,600
(for intentional assault, extortion,)

428
00:44:08,600 --> 00:44:09,880
(selling substandard products,)

429
00:44:09,880 --> 00:44:11,430
(and attempted illegal border crossing.)

430
00:44:11,460 --> 00:44:12,970
(Lyu Danshun was sentenced to 6 years)

431
00:44:12,970 --> 00:44:14,140
(for perjury)

432
00:44:14,140 --> 00:44:16,300
(and harboring and concealing.)

433
00:44:16,760 --> 00:44:18,210
(Kong Tai was sentenced to 12 years)

434
00:44:18,210 --> 00:44:19,920
(for organizing
illegal border crossing.)

435
00:44:19,920 --> 00:44:20,570
(Other members)

436
00:44:20,570 --> 00:44:21,810
(played a minor auxiliary role)

